body:
Because I like you - WinterIron

Fandom: Marvel

Prompt:“ Why are you doing this?”

Words: 321

James Buchanan Barnes could always get really caring and protective when he loved someone platonically or romantically.

That’s why Steve quickly noticed that his best friend had a huge crush on a certain billionaire.

Tony however was mostly confused by Buckys behaviour. James giving him things from the top shelf, a coffee often waiting for him in the morning, waking up with a blanket around his shoulders when Tony felt asleep in the workshop or James bringing him something to eat and drink when he was working without a break at a project.

Of course Tony enjoyed such a treatment but he didn’t trusted it. Every time Bucky did something for him the mechanic waited for a request. He was used to that people only did things for him so they could get something in return.

But James never asked for anything. That confused Tony even more. It didn’t make sense for Stark, because Bucky had no reason to be so nice to him.

So one day Tony snapped:“Why are you doing this? It makes no sense!”

Bucky, who had just placed a glass of water on the table, looked confused at the other man:“What do you mean?”

“This and everything else! You always do these nice things for me, look after me, but you never ask for anything in return.”

“I like you. Isn’t that reason enough to do these things?” Bucky replied simply.

“What?” the mechanic asked dumbfounded.

James smiled:“I look after you because I like you. To be completely honest I love you.”

Now a slight blush became visible on Tonys cheeks, which made Bucky smile even more.

“Really? This is not some kind of joke?” Stark asked unsure.

“I would never joke about something like this.”

“Then…uhm…then how about dinner this evening? Just the two of us. ” Tony suggested.

“Sounds lovely.” Bucky replied before placing a kiss on the smaller mans forehead.

@mouse-the-human, @the-painter-and-the-poet, @mistressstrange

Scarlett Johansson, who has appeared in six movies as Black Widow, is finally landing a $15 million payday for an upcoming stand-alone film centered on the Marvel superheroine, The Hollywood Reporter has learned.

That salary is what Chris Evans and Chris Hemsworth each earned for playing Captain America and Thor, respectively, in this year’s Avengers: Infinity War. Evans and Hemsworth also nabbed…

summary: Anyone looking for a pen pal? I’m taking a break before a masters program and would love to make new friends!
body:
Anyone looking for a pen pal? I’m taking a break before a masters program and would love to make new friends!

Basic info: 21 year old girl living in Dubai, avid interest of all things MCU, books, and recently kpop and kdrama.

Absolutely love sending a receiving postcards so hit me up, esp if you’re a mutual or follower!

Message me please!
